      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I can sense the depth of your emotional pain and the overwhelming feelings of shame and despair you're experiencing. Losing a business can be devastating, and it's completely understandable that you're struggling to find a way out of this difficult situation. Your feelings of worthlessness and anger are valid, and I'm here to offer you a non-judgmental space to process your emotions.",
